<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:11:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列宣布约旦河西岸货币兑换恐怖组织扣押哈马斯数百万资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</link><description>以色列军队突袭了约旦河西岸的 9 个货币兑换分行，逮捕了 21 名涉嫌向哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织转移资金的巴勒斯坦人。巴勒斯坦人报告称，袭击期间发生冲突，造成一人死亡、多人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 11:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗革命卫队主席誓言在以色列杀害高级顾问后“铲除犹太复国主义政权”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/irgc-chief-vows-to-eradicate-zionist-regime-after-alleged-israeli-killing-of-top-adviser/0000018c-afe2-d45c-a98e-afeee70e0000</link><description>伊朗最高领袖哈梅内伊在叙利亚空袭中丧生的赛义德·拉齐·穆萨维的葬礼上主持祈祷。以色列军队拒绝就穆萨维之死发表评论，但表示已采取一切必要行动来保卫国家</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 11:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/irgc-chief-vows-to-eradicate-zionist-regime-after-alleged-israeli-killing-of-top-adviser/0000018c-afe2-d45c-a98e-afeee70e0000</guid></item><item><title>当 DNA 失败时，这些以色列人类学家正在帮助识别 10 月 7 日死者的身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/when-dna-fails-these-israeli-anthropologists-are-helping-identify-the-october-7-dead/0000018c-afe7-d45c-a98e-afef12ea0000</link><description>Israel Hershkovitz 教授、Hila May 博士和特拉维夫大学的体质人类学专家正在与法医病理学家合作，帮助识别 10 月 7 日的受害者并确定他们的死因，并为未来针对哈马斯恐怖分子建立案件</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/when-dna-fails-these-israeli-anthropologists-are-helping-identify-the-october-7-dead/0000018c-afe7-d45c-a98e-afef12ea0000</guid></item><item><title>这位犹太学者认为散居海外的犹太人必须接受流亡才能拯救犹太教</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-jewish-scholar-believes-diaspora-jews-must-embrace-exile-to-save-judaism/0000018c-af75-d45c-a98e-af7d47ac0000</link><description>绍尔·马吉德曾经是加沙地带的犹太定居者，但如今他是一位受人尊敬的犹太研究教授，他将自己的世界观定义为“反犹太复国主义”。他的立场设想以色列尊重所有人民的历史并放弃犹太复国主义作为“仅限犹太人”的意识形态</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-jewish-scholar-believes-diaspora-jews-must-embrace-exile-to-save-judaism/0000018c-af75-d45c-a98e-af7d47ac0000</guid></item><item><title>决定泄露后以色列最高法院将加快对司法政变法的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-set-to-expedite-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law-after-decision-leak/0000018c-af76-db94-afbd-af7f3c1b0000</link><description>报告称，八名法官中的大多数支持废除该法律，七名法官反对。司法部长亚里夫·莱文回应称，高等法院不应“在战争期间发布有争议的裁决，即使是在其法官之间”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 09:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-set-to-expedite-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law-after-decision-leak/0000018c-af76-db94-afbd-af7f3c1b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵惊醒后开枪，轻伤战友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-opens-fire-after-waking-up-with-a-start-lightly-wounds-fellow-troops/0000018c-ac24-d22d-a3dd-bd7d13250000</link><description>由于这名士兵的健康状况，尚未就该事件接受军队询问。每天，数十名士兵被带出加沙接受心理健康官员和精神病学家的检查和治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-opens-fire-after-waking-up-with-a-start-lightly-wounds-fellow-troops/0000018c-ac24-d22d-a3dd-bd7d13250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周三在加沙战斗中丧生的三名以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</link><description>以色列军方还表示，加沙地带南部和中部还有其他士兵受重伤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗“独立”代理人的袭击增加了与以色列和美国发生直接冲突的可能性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</link><description>自以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，德黑兰一直避免与以色列和美国直接对抗。但“抵抗轴心”成员所表现出的独立性使得伊斯兰共和国更难维持合理的推诿，并有可能将其拖入冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后，以色列极端正统派部长花了一天时间为地方选举进行政治活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</link><description>当以色列陷入混乱时，梅厄·波鲁什正忙着做交易，以确保他的联合托拉犹太教党和他的儿子埃拉德市长以色列·波鲁什在即将到来的选举中的利益</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队击落从黎巴嫩飞越以色列北部上空的无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-live/suicide-drone-hits-buildings-on-golan-israel-on-very-high-alert-on-lebanon-border/0000018c-ae77-db94-afbd-ae7f8d860000</link><description>以色列外交部长：只要埃尔多安还是土耳其总统，以色列大使就不会回来 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：以色列袭击导致加沙 50 名巴勒斯坦人丧生 ■ 以色列国防军称在加沙城发现了更多隧道 ■ 自杀式无人机损坏戈兰高地的建筑物高地 ■ 以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的名字 ■ 巴勒斯坦人：六人在约旦河西岸无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生；至少 130 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 21,110 人死亡，55,243 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 03:39:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-live/suicide-drone-hits-buildings-on-golan-israel-on-very-high-alert-on-lebanon-border/0000018c-ae77-db94-afbd-ae7f8d860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列副总检察长表示，本-格维尔部非法发放了 14,000 张枪支许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-distributed-14-000-gun-licenses-illegally-israels-deputy-ag-says/0000018c-acea-d45c-a98e-afeef7530000</link><description>本-格维尔的国家安全部利用加沙战争来发挥“创意”，规避有关枪支许可证和所有权的现有规定。司法部认为违法后将其关闭</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-distributed-14-000-gun-licenses-illegally-israels-deputy-ag-says/0000018c-acea-d45c-a98e-afeef7530000</guid></item><item><title>五名以色列士兵因在约旦河西岸袭击巴勒斯坦人而被定居者积极分子部队开除</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/five-soldiers-dismissed-from-idf-from-settler-activist-unit-for-assaulting-palestinians/0000018c-ac4b-d22c-a98c-fc6fea220000</link><description>根据巴勒斯坦人的证词，袭击者剥光他们的衣服并殴打他们，在他们身上撒尿，并在他们身上熄灭香烟。以色列国防军最近停止了该部队的业务活动，该部队从西岸前哨基地招募定居青年服兵役</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 21:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/five-soldiers-dismissed-from-idf-from-settler-activist-unit-for-assaulting-palestinians/0000018c-ac4b-d22c-a98c-fc6fea220000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，加沙辛贝特消息来源警告哈马斯将于 10 月初对以色列发动重大袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/shin-bet-source-in-gaza-reportedly-warned-of-major-hamas-attack-in-early-october/0000018c-acab-d22c-a98c-fcefb17e0000</link><description>据12频道报道，消息来源的负责人将这一信息进行了传递，但最终只停留在较低级别，没有到达更高级别的当局。辛贝特对此回应称，“所有现有信息都将受到审查”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/shin-bet-source-in-gaza-reportedly-warned-of-major-hamas-attack-in-early-october/0000018c-acab-d22c-a98c-fcefb17e0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列高等法院法官准备废除去年夏天通过的关键司法政变法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/report-high-court-justices-poised-to-nullify-key-judicial-coup-law-passed-last-summer/0000018c-ac99-d22d-a3dd-bdf985e20000</link><description>报告称，15 名法官中有 8 名支持废除该法律，该法律取消了法院对政府决定进行司法审查的能力。最终裁决将在未来几周内公布。以色列司法当局拒绝“承认”“未经证实的泄密”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/report-high-court-justices-poised-to-nullify-key-judicial-coup-law-passed-last-summer/0000018c-ac99-d22d-a3dd-bdf985e20000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨反击本格维尔，但表示他将继续留在以色列紧急政府“以赢得战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/gantz-pushes-back-against-ben-gvir-says-hell-remain-in-emergency-govt-to-win-war/0000018c-ac5c-d22c-a98c-fc7c07010000</link><description>极右翼部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔决定不延长以色列监狱管理局专员的任期，这违反了甘茨政党与利库德集团在 10 月 7 日战争开始后进入紧急政府的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 18:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/gantz-pushes-back-against-ben-gvir-says-hell-remain-in-emergency-govt-to-win-war/0000018c-ac5c-d22c-a98c-fc7c07010000</guid></item><item><title>开枪赋予了我力量。携带一个是我在以色列感觉最不安全的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-27/ty-article/.highlight/shooting-a-gun-empowered-me-carrying-one-is-the-least-safe-ive-felt-in-israel/0000018c-ac0f-d462-afbe-accf685a0000</link><description>我只是希望数以万计新获得许可的以色列枪支拥有者——无论是否经过授权方批准——都知道他们刚刚购买的武器的重量，并对这种力量保持敬畏和恐惧</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 17:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-27/ty-article/.highlight/shooting-a-gun-empowered-me-carrying-one-is-the-least-safe-ive-felt-in-israel/0000018c-ac0f-d462-afbe-accf685a0000</guid></item><item><title>“加沙死亡现在在以色列是一个禁忌话题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-27/ty-article-podcast/death-in-gaza-is-a-taboo-subject-in-israel-right-now/0000018c-aaec-d885-abdf-feeec86a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 17:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-27/ty-article-podcast/death-in-gaza-is-a-taboo-subject-in-israel-right-now/0000018c-aaec-d885-abdf-feeec86a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的新型地狱：《国土报》关于难以想象的现实的重要文章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/war-in-gaza-though-gazan-eyes-read-the-best-haaretz-articles-from-an-unthinkable-reality/0000018c-abf1-d22d-a3dd-bff9a4b20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 16:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/war-in-gaza-though-gazan-eyes-read-the-best-haaretz-articles-from-an-unthinkable-reality/0000018c-abf1-d22d-a3dd-bff9a4b20000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩裔澳大利亚人、他的妻子和真主党成员兄弟在以色列空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/lebanese-australian-his-wife-and-hezbollah-member-brother-killed-in-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-ac06-d22d-a3dd-bd7f8f280000</link><description>据报道，这次空袭发生在以色列和真主党之间最近在黎巴嫩边境爆发敌对行动之际。澳大利亚外交部表示已获悉该报道并正在寻求证实</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 16:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/lebanese-australian-his-wife-and-hezbollah-member-brother-killed-in-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-ac06-d22d-a3dd-bd7f8f280000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其领导人称以色列总理“与希特勒没有什么不同”后，埃尔多安和内塔尼亚胡互斥</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/erdogan-netanyahu-trade-barbs-after-turkey-leader-compares-israeli-pm-to-hitler/0000018c-abcf-d45c-a98e-abcf6fcd0000</link><description>“内塔尼亚胡所做的事情比希特勒所做的事情还少吗？”事实并非如此，”埃尔多安说。内塔尼亚胡回应称，埃尔多安应该是最后一个对以色列说教的人，称他正在对库尔德人实施种族灭绝，并保持着监禁记者的世界纪录</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/erdogan-netanyahu-trade-barbs-after-turkey-leader-compares-israeli-pm-to-hitler/0000018c-abcf-d45c-a98e-abcf6fcd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>